>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Sticky pinned main menu, logo and widgets.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">CSS Superfish multi-level dropdown pinned menu<strong>.<\\/strong><\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Responsive multi-level menu support, flexible and cross-browser compatibility.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Tableless design and 100% CSS based.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Built by advance HTML5 and CSS3.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Lightweight and fast-loading.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Logo as Image with configuration parameters.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Built-in Google Fonts (<strong>more fonts - 650+ available only with Qucikstart Package<\\/strong>).<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Built-in social media icons for the popular social networking sites including Twitter, Facebook, Google Plus, Youtube, LinkedIn and more...<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">2 layout options: 2 columns (content + right), 1 column (content).<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Typography Page.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Joomla! tags com_tags layout override -&nbsp;show articles intro text and item image with link to the full article in the result page for Joomla Tags.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">A lot Module Positions.&nbsp;All module positions are fully collapsible.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Cross-Browser Support - Transport Joomla template work great with all modern browsers like Firefox, Chrome, Safari, Opera and Internet Explorer 9+.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">Heading: h1, h2, h3, h4 and h5.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">SEO SEF Optimised Layout. Optimized code for Search Engines which helps in SEO.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">SEO Breadcrumbs with Microdata Google - this will give a nice category-display in the Google search results.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\">And more features,&nbsp;some only available in the Premium Version with quickstart package:<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<h3>JooFood Joomla Template Quickstart Instalation Package<\\/h3>\\n<h3>What is quickstart package?<\\/h3>\\n<p>\\\"Quickstart Package\\\" is a JooFood Joomla Template + Joomla 3 + all content, all modules, all components and settings used in <strong><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/demo.joothemes.net\\/joomla3\\/joofood\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">demo site<\\/a><\\/strong>. After installation You will get exactly the same as demo page.<\\/p>\\n<h3>How to install Quickstart package?<\\/h3>\\n<p>Quickstart Package install exactly the same as a normal Joomla! installation package. (To get know more about technical requirements to run Joomla! please visit: Joomla technical requirements).<\\/p>\\n<p><strong>Quickstart will save your time and work. You will get exactly the same as demo page <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/demo.joothemes.net\\/joomla3\\/joofood\\\">https:\\/\\/demo.joothemes.net\\/joomla3\\/joofood<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<h3>Quickstart package extra features,&nbsp;component, modules and plugins:<\\/h3>\\n<ul>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>Gallery plugin and module<\\/strong> (<strong>available in Qucikstart Package<\\/strong>).&nbsp;(Sigplus Image Gallery Plus is a straightforward way to add image or photo galleries to a Joomla article with a simple syntax. It takes a matter of minutes to set up a gallery but those who are looking for a powerful gallery solution will not be disappointed either: sigplus is suitable for both beginner and advanced users.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>Built-in 650+ Google Fonts<\\/strong> (<strong>available only with Qucikstart Package<\\/strong>).<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>JUNews Ultra Pro module<\\/strong>&nbsp;(override layouts for JooFood template). JUNews Ultra Pro module display latest news (Joomla Articles) with full control over all elements, cool effects, rich backend configs covering layout, auto thumbnail creating, images resizing, numbering articles, sorting ect...&nbsp;(available only with Qucikstart Package).&nbsp;Best Joomla module for news, articles, YouTube and RSS with many options. Fast performs and mostly optimization for over 100.000 articles! Make you easy and simple templates! In one module, a greater functionality, which replaces a number of modules. The module has the ability to create different patterns (templates), thus you can change the type of modules as you like and use the module on the news portals, on the portfolio or personal site. (JUNewsUltra Pro news module and our override template for Clients Testimonials view available only with Qucikstart Package).<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>JWeb Portfolio Display responsive grid module<\\/strong> for Joomla that helps create a portfolio easily with filter, lightbox effect, page details and categories. There are lots of parameters and you can set them easily. This awesome module is responsive and seo optimized. Perfect solution for you to create your own portfolio on Joomla 3.x CMS.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>JComments<\\/strong> - a powerful and easy to use AJAX based comment system for Joomla with flexible ACL, smiles, BBCodes and avatars support. Working on this release took extra eight months, all this effort was spent to make the component more stable and usable. Considerable time was allotted for code optimization and improved compatibility to third-party extensions.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>Joomla! tags com_tags layout override<\\/strong> - show articles intro text and item image with link to the full article in the result page for Joomla Tags.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>Akeeba Backup Core<\\/strong> -&nbsp;is the most widely used open-source backup component for the Joomla! CMS. Its mission is simple: create a site backup that can be restored on any Joomla!-capable server, making it ideal not only for backups but also for site transfers or even deploying sites to your clients\' servers. Akeeba Backup creates a full backup of your site in a single archive. The archive contains all the files, a database snapshot and an installer similar in function to the standard Joomla! installer.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>JCE editor - the best WYSiWYG editor for Joomla! <\\/strong>An award-winning, configurable WYSIWYG editor for Joomla! based on Moxiecode\'s TinyMCE. Includes advanced Image, File and Link handling, plugin support, and an Administration interface for editor configuration.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;\\\"><strong>Extra SEO SEF plugin - EFSEO -<\\/strong>&nbsp;automatically generates description meta tags by pulling text from the content to help with SEO. It also gives you the ability to set different title configurations. EFSEO is a SEO extension for Joomla! with which you can control all important metadata manually and automatically. The handling of the metadata in Joomla! has never been so easy!&nbsp;With the plugin you may change and add meta information (title, description, keywords, generator and robots) easily in the frontend and with the component in the backend. It does not matter which component you use. The plugin is active on every page of a Joomla! website and may be used correspondingly.<\\/li>\\n<li style=\\\"font