(48, 4, 1, '', '2022-05-27 07:31:03', 5, 9137, 'b60e73dc43812bc36055d5edb58bd0b5cd373ee8', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":\"68\",\"title\":\"Tuy\\u1ec3n d\\u1ee5ng\",\"alias\":\"tuya-n-da-ng\",\"introtext\":\"<h2><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">M\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail-article\\\">\\r\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh\\u00a0cho ph\\u00f2ng ban Marketing\\u00a0bao g\\u1ed3m:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Ki\\u1ec3m tra t\\u00ednh h\\u1ee3p l\\u1ec7 v\\u00e0 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n thanh to\\u00e1n c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ee9ng t\\u1eeb, h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Marketing tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi tr\\u00ecnh k\\u00fd Unit head.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Ki\\u1ec3m tra v\\u00e0 thanh to\\u00e1n chi ph\\u00ed c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c, v\\u00e9 m\\u00e1y bay, kh\\u00e1ch s\\u1ea1n c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">So\\u1ea1n th\\u1ea3o v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd S\\u1edf C\\u00f4ng Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u00e1c ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean to\\u00e0n qu\\u1ed1c<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Tham gia c\\u00e1c cu\\u1ed9c h\\u1ecdp c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng Marketing v\\u00e0 ghi l\\u1ea1i bi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n cu\\u1ed9c h\\u1ecdp<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Theo d\\u00f5i l\\u1ecbch h\\u1ecdp c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng Marketing v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7t ph\\u00f2ng h\\u1ecdp<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c c\\u1ee7a ph\\u00f2ng Marketing bao g\\u1ed3m thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng v\\u00e0 v\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng ph\\u1ea9m<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch s\\u1ed1 li\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m, d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Thu th\\u1eadp th\\u00f4ng tin d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u: sales, kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng, s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m, \\u2026\\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o cho ph\\u00f2ng Marketing theo y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Theo d\\u00f5i v\\u00e0 b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng qu\\u1ea3ng c\\u00e1o tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed (Digital media channels), qu\\u1ea3ng c\\u00e1o ngo\\u00e0i tr\\u1eddi (OOH), quan h\\u1ec7 b\\u00e1o ch\\u00ed \\u2013 c\\u00f4ng ch\\u00fang (Public Relation) v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c, t\\u00e0i tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u00e1c (Co-Branding, Partnership, Sponsorship).<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">C\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c kh\\u00e1c:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng n\\u1ed9i b\\u1ed9 li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u v\\u00e0 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c kh\\u00e1c theo y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u c\\u1ee7a Tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng b\\u1ed9 ph\\u1eadn.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Y\\u00eau C\\u1ea7u:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">T\\u1ed1t nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc chuy\\u00ean ng\\u00e0nh Marketing, Truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng v\\u00e0 Qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb kinh doanh.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">C\\u00f3 kinh nghi\\u1ec7m \\u1edf v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u00f4ng th\\u1ea1o ti\\u1ebfng Anh giao ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfng Anh chuy\\u00ean ng\\u00e0nh Marketing<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u00f4ng th\\u1ea1o MS Office\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch s\\u1ed1 li\\u1ec7u\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">K\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng giao ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e0m ph\\u00e1n t\\u1ed1t\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">N\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o v\\u00e0 tinh th\\u1ea7n tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m cao<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Tinh th\\u1ea7n h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi cao<\\/span><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">Th\\u1eddi gian l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c:\\u00a09h00 - 18h00 (ngh\\u1ec9 T7, CN)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; color: #000000;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m:\\u00a016 Tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110\\u1ecbnh, ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng