(49, 3, 1, '', '2022-05-27 07:34:32', 5, 5136, '31ae7af9c009412fa78642180455fd8a383f6755', '{\"id\":3,\"asset_id\":\"67\",\"title\":\"Khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u00e3i s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\",\"alias\":\"khuya-n-ma-i-sa-n-pha-m\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\">C\\u00e1ch n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap qu\\u00e1n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u00eam kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0o nh\\u1eefng khung gi\\u1edd \\u201c\\u1ebf\\u201d h\\u00e0ng ng\\u00e0y v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 nh\\u01b0 kho\\u1ea3ng th\\u1eddi gian t\\u1eeb 9h s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn 10h s\\u00e1ng, 3h \\u0111\\u1ebfn 5h chi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1eb3ng h\\u1ea1n. Nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng s\\u1ebd l\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u1ea7y ch\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ed1ng trong nh\\u1eefng gi\\u1edd th\\u1ea5p \\u0111i\\u1ec3m v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ti\\u00eau th\\u1ee5 nguy\\u00ean v\\u1eadt li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00f4i h\\u01a1n, gi\\u1ea3m chi ph\\u00ed b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n, t\\u0103ng doanh thu ng\\u00e0y.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/suno.vn\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/02\\/bi-quyet-marketing-website-nha-hang-hieu-qua-dip-le-tet-3-1-1024x536-1.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\">Nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u01b0 l\\u1ec5, t\\u1ebft, ng\\u00e0y khai tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng tung ra ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u00e3i h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn. V\\u00ec l\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t n\\u00ean th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ee9ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u00f3 th\\u1eddi gian \\u0111\\u1ec3 r\\u1ee7 b\\u1ea1n b\\u00e8 hay ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi th\\u00e2n gh\\u00e9 qua.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\">Tuy nhi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ec3 khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch h\\u00e0ng \\u0111i theo nh\\u00f3m b\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n cho nh\\u00f3m tr\\u00ean bao nhi\\u00eau ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady s\\u1ebd mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 cho ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1edbn h\\u01a1n.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\"><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cafebiz.cafebizcdn.vn\\/2019\\/6\\/24\\/photo-3-1561388759801918950988.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Nh\\u1eefng chi\\u00eau \\u201cm\\u00f3c t\\u00fai\\u201d t\\u1ea1i c\\u1eeda h\\u00e0ng th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n nhanh: Th\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u01a1n r\\u1ed1i m\\u00f9, s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m  \\u201cm\\u1ed3i\\u201d, upsize mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed, khuy\\u1ebfn m\\u00e3i quanh n\\u0103m\\u2026\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\\\">V\\u00e0o nh\\u1eefng th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u01b0: l\\u1ec5, t\\u1ebft, ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh chi \\u00e2n,.. C\\u1eeda h\\u00e0ng s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u nh\\u1eefng \\u01b0u \\u0111\\u00e3 cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng, nh\\u1eefng m\\u00f3n qu\\u00e0 h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn d\\u00e0nh t\\u1eb7ng cho b\\u1ea1n!<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2022-05-25 02:32:21\",\"created_by\":\"5\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2022-05-27 07:34:32\",\"modified_by\":\"5\",\"checked_out\":\"5\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2022-05-27 07:32:50\",\"publish_up\":\"2022-05-25 02:32:21\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 0