(71, 7, 1, '', '2022-05-27 09:30:56', 5, 11436, '988c7f3afd6fcc4084804633e5351160846f561a', '{\"id\":7,\"asset_id\":\"86\",\"title\":\"Tuy\\u1ec3n d\\u1ee5ng\",\"alias\":\"tuya-n-da-ng\",\"introtext\":\"<h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Tuy\\u1ec3n d\\u1ee5ng nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean Fast Food:<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">M\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail-article\\\">\\r\\n<ul style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Thi\\u1ebft l\\u1eadp\\/tri\\u1ec3n khai\\/th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n\\/gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t c\\u00e1c qui tr\\u00ecnh, qui \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to\\u00e0n cho c\\u00f4ng ty nh\\u01b0: An to\\u00e0n lao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, An to\\u00e0n PCCC cho t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean,<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c c\\u00e1c bu\\u1ed5i hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n, chia s\\u1ebb v\\u1ec1 An to\\u00e0n lao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, PCCC cho c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1c b\\u1ed9 c\\u00f4ng nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean c\\u00f4ng ty<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Thi\\u1ebft l\\u1eadp\\/tri\\u1ec3n khai\\/th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n\\/gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t c\\u00e1c qui tr\\u00ecnh, qui \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe cho t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c ph\\u00f2ng ch\\u1ed1ng d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh nguy hi\\u1ec3m c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 an to\\u00e0n duy tr\\u00ec ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng kinh doanh (d\\u1ecbch Covid19\\u2026)<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Tri\\u1ec3n khai, qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd, gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t v\\u00e0 b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o vi\\u1ec7c kh\\u00e1m s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 h\\u00e0ng n\\u0103m cho nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Gi\\u00e1m s\\u00e1t vi\\u1ec7c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebft ki\\u1ec7m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">T\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n c\\u00e1c gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p an ninh n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cho C\\u00f4ng ty<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd\\/b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o\\/ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111o\\u00e0n c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1n li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn: x\\u1eed l\\u00fd r\\u00e1c th\\u1ea3i, n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ea3i theo quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi b\\u1ed9 ph\\u1eadn QA \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7n ph\\u00e1p an to\\u00e0n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m, c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf h\\u1ea1 t\\u1ea7ng \\u0111\\u00e1p \\u1ee9ng theo c\\u00e1c ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n ch\\u1ee9ng ch\\u1ec9 ISO 22000<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Tri\\u1ec3n khai k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o \\u0111\\u1ecbnh k\\u1ef3 c\\u00e1c qui \\u0111\\u1ecbnh li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn SHE, c\\u00e1c qui \\u0111\\u1ecbnh theo ti\\u00eau chu\\u1ea9n ISO 2200<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 trong vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh, cung c\\u1ea5p c\\u00e1c d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u cho c\\u00e1c ph\\u00f2ng ban.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi ph\\u00f2ng HRBP trong c\\u00e1c s\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ec7n c\\u00f4ng ty<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">L\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u1ed1i l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c v\\u1edbi ban qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd Khu c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, ban qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd khu kinh t\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 quan ban ng\\u00e0nh kh\\u00e1c<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">X\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng m\\u1ed1i quan h\\u1ec7, ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p t\\u1ed1t v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 quan ban ng\\u00e0nh nh\\u1eb1m gi\\u00fap Jollibee nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a. K\\u1ecbp th\\u1eddi tri\\u1ec3n khai c\\u00e1c quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t\\u1eeb ban ng\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn Ban qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd C\\u00f4ng ty<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n