(80, 14, 1, '', '2022-05-30 12:15:28', 5, 4867, '17310d63992ef59e2681f7f210ce156e4e1146af', '{\"id\":14,\"asset_id\":\"93\",\"title\":\"Hambuger t\\u00f4m\",\"alias\":\"hambuger-ta-m\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">B\\u00e1nh hamburger c\\u00f3 ngu\\u1ed3n g\\u1ed1c t\\u1eeb t\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 Hamburg (\\u0110\\u1ee9c).\\u00a0 Hamburger l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n bao g\\u1ed3m b\\u00e1nh m\\u00ec, th\\u1ecbt xay ho\\u1eb7c th\\u1ecbt hun kh\\u00f3i k\\u00e8m rau c\\u1ee7 k\\u1eb9p \\u1edf gi\\u1eefa v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0103n c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi khoai t\\u00e2y chi\\u00ean ho\\u1eb7c ph\\u00f4 mai,\\u2026<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\"><img style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/dakhoayhocquocte.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/11\\/1-cai-banh-hamburger-bao-nhieu-calo.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"1 c\\u00e1i b\\u00e1nh humburger bao nhi\\u00eau calo\\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">V\\u1eady\\u00a0<strong>hamburger bao nhi\\u00eau calo?<\\/strong>\\u00a0c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng cho bi\\u1ebft: \\u201ctrong 1 chi\\u1ebfc b\\u00e1nh hamburger c\\u1ee1 nh\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a kho\\u1ea3ng 455 calo v\\u00e0 26 gam ch\\u1ea5t b\\u00e9o v\\u00e0 13 gam ch\\u1ea5t b\\u00e9o b\\u00e3o h\\u00f2a. C\\u00f2n n\\u1ebfu c\\u1ee1 l\\u1edbn c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn 733 calo v\\u00e0 41 gram ch\\u1ea5t b\\u00e9o.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 1