(85, 17, 1, '', '2022-05-30 12:22:11', 5, 6112, 'ffd40302242b79e91ba589eb9ffc0ff509245dd1', '{\"id\":17,\"asset_id\":96,\"title\":\"B\\u00e1nh Maracon\",\"alias\":\"ba-nh-maracon\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Macaron l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i b\\u00e1nh ng\\u1ecdt d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean\\u00a0<a style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\" title=\\\"b\\u00e1nh tr\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/vi.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/B%C3%A1nh_tr%E1%BB%A9ng_%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\\\">b\\u00e1nh tr\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng<\\/a>\\u00a0(m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i b\\u00e1nh b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00e1ng mi\\u1ec7ng \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng c\\u1ee7a \\u1ea9m th\\u1ef1c Ph\\u00e1p, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e1nh l\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u l\\u00ean v\\u00e0 th\\u00eam ch\\u00fat \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u00f9ng ch\\u00fat axit t\\u1eeb chanh t\\u00e2y hay gi\\u1ea5m).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\">Ngo\\u00e0i l\\u00f2ng tr\\u1eafng tr\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u00e1nh l\\u00ean, macaron c\\u00f2n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c nguy\\u00ean li\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng b\\u1ed9t, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0u th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m, nh\\u1edd v\\u1eady m\\u00e0 b\\u00e1nh tr\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 c\\u00f9ng b\\u1eaft m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea5p d\\u1eabn.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\\\"><img class=\\\"lazy\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tgdd.vn\\/2021\\/05\\/content\\/1-800x500-12.jpg\\\" alt